0","tid":390122,"uid":129058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:33:22.000Z","msg":"保方？<br />\n馬甸尼？<br />\n大簡？"},{"pid":"0c2739d9b75219c8104086374d5d84d3ba903c6d","tid":390122,"uid":15724,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左大猩猩全部都係攻擊球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬甸尼，大簡，保方，舒米高等真係who fucking cares咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但攻擊球員又無巴迪高，基斯普，托迪，迪比阿路，魯爾等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確係少後防 我認為保方同卡斯可直接取代大猩猩個位 大簡係後防惟一拎到金球 馬甸尼係一個後衛既時代 呢堆都認同<br />\n<br />\n但攻擊果堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔係up一堆舊人名就叫球王嫁 問心 你講果堆攻擊球員拍埋樓主果堆真係輸晒 完全唔入流 特別係基斯普同raul <br />\n不過樓主有啲資料有錯 朗拿度係國家隊多獎 但球會冇咩獎 得2，3次聯賽冠軍 歐聯都未拎過過"},{"pid":"d255f2e5aba9fb8078ce7554d1dbb9da2b807a44","tid":390122,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfeb69bf2c6392c0d513e7c8d2061d7330b0b16","tid":390122,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb117a1e72d1624e9008a38e77f9c30fc016955e","tid":390122,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffaf2650ac49bc3706d08530fbd2d6309b50b36","tid":390122,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:47:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab93c31a158ee2bd96c7a60a3b54c236708de40d","tid":390122,"uid":15724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432eb5b2cb41062