faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無機會表演又點做到球王呀醒目<br />\n<br />\n保方講真佢霸住個位咁多年，阻住新星上位，完全無球王風範</blockquote><br />\n淨係三屆世界盃都有表現加埋球會水準穩定已經長過你所講卡卡同史奈達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n卡卡離開米蘭已經打唔番啦， 國家隊又甚少建樹。<br />\n史奈達踢完三冠同之後嗰屆世盃叫最高峰， 之後仲有咩佳作？ 佢咗踢土耳其低水準聯賽， 你都冇睇啦啱唔啱呀， 請問佢兩位憑咩令你覺得球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就係嗰幾年？ 如果講幾年figo都好勁喎， 李華度呢？<br />\n你仲話佢冇國家榮譽唔應該入選， 如果用呢個標準乜美斯有咩， 我真係唔知你準則係咩， 都幾自打嘴巴<br />\n我都唔知你點睇幾廿年波， 根本白睇定係鳩吹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過算啦你連保方都可以話霸住個位呢啲咁垃圾嘅說話都噏得出我就知道認真咗， 係咁。"},{"pid":"deddad068e87d99869f5e6be3c57202c5be197c2","tid":390122,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>享利都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國家隊零表現</blockquote><br />\n點都唔係零啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b35d4548cc7bf2d8b547fadafacf9ed144607bf","tid":390122,"uid":53774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"大空翼"},{"pid":"e3aa5843a3c901a206bceaf7c2c33004890e4ffe","tid":390122,"uid":54945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>享利都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n國家隊零表現</blockquote><br />\n點都唔係零啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n話哂都一手送法國入決賽周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b67c7e24431c62070e6c677922dff694255ced","tid":390122,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T02:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實你份名單冇保方係冇人會承認</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇保方呢個LIST根本係垃圾"},{"pid":"8ab8a2857c7130658e85020f28e48851b5c7bd96","tid":390122,"uid":2